---
// WhatWeDo section - displays core service offerings with SVG bullet indicators
---

<section class="what-we-do">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="services-content">
            <h2 class="brutal-heading-lg">What We Do</h2>
            <p class="intro-text">GST unlocks enterprise value through expert business technology advisory.</p>

            <ul class="services-list">
                <li>
                    <span>Buy-side and sell-side technical diligence</span>
                    <img src="/images/logo/gst-delta-icon-teal-stroke-thick.svg" alt="Service checkmark - Buy-side and sell-side technical diligence" class="bullet-icon" loading="lazy" />
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Architecture and platform assessments</span>
                    <img src="/images/logo/gst-delta-icon-teal-stroke-thick.svg" alt="Service checkmark - Architecture and platform assessments" class="bullet-icon" loading="lazy" />
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Security, compliance, and operational risk evaluation</span>
                    <img src="/images/logo/gst-delta-icon-teal-stroke-thick.svg" alt="Service checkmark - Security, compliance, and operational risk evaluation" class="bullet-icon" loading="lazy" />
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Product development and execution roadmaps</span>
                    <img src="/images/logo/gst-delta-icon-teal-stroke-thick.svg" alt="Service checkmark - Product development, modernization and execution roadmaps" class="bullet-icon" loading="lazy" />
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Independent advisory for executives and boards</span>
                    <img src="/images/logo/gst-delta-icon-teal-stroke-thick.svg" alt="Service checkmark - Independent advisory for executives and boards" class="bullet-icon" loading="lazy" />
                </li>
            </ul>

            <p class="closing-text">Clear findings. Decision-ready outputs. Practical next steps.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* Component styles following design system patterns */
    .what-we-do {
        padding: var(--spacing-3xl) 0;
        background: transparent;
        position: relative;
    }

    .services-content {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: right;
    }

    .brutal-heading-lg {
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    }

    .intro-text {
        font-size: var(--text-lg);
        font-family: monospace;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .services-list {
        list-style: none;
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--gap-wide);
    }

    .services-list li {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: var(--spacing-lg);
        justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .bullet-icon {
        width: 1.25rem;
        height: 1.25rem;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .services-list li span {
        font-size: var(--text-base);
        font-family: monospace;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .closing-text {
        font-size: var(--text-base);
        font-family: monospace;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
        padding-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
        border-top: 2px solid var(--border-light);
    }

    .closing-text::before {
        content: '// ';
        color: var(--color-primary);
        font-weight: 900;
    }

    /* Dark theme support */
    :global(html.dark-theme) .what-we-do {
        background: transparent;
    }

    :global(html.dark-theme) .closing-text {
        border-top-color: var(--border-dark-default);
    }

    /* Responsive design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .what-we-do {
            padding: var(--spacing-2xl) 0;
        }

        .intro-text {
            font-size: var(--text-base);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
        }

        .services-list {
            gap: var(--gap-normal);
        }

        .bullet-icon {
            width: 1rem;
            height: 1rem;
        }

        .services-list li span {
            font-size: var(--text-small);
        }

        .closing-text {
            font-size: var(--text-small);
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .what-we-do {
            padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
        }

        .services-list li {
            gap: var(--spacing-md);
        }
    }
</style>
